#Authentication User Stories

##Register and validate
User Registration:

As a user, I want to register an account so that I can access banking services.
As a user, I want to provide my personal information and upload my ID documents during registration.
As a user, I want to receive a confirmation email upon successful registration.

KYC Verification:
As a user, I want my identity documents to be verified automatically so that my account can be activated quickly.
As a user, I want to be notified if there are any issues with my documents.

Account Setup:
As a user, I want to set up my personal account details, such as setting a password and security questions.
As a user, I want to receive a welcome message once my account is fully set up and verified.

